{"tid":835780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實習近平識唔識英文？","createTime":"2018-09-25T07:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T14:10:45.000Z","uid":25535,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"888e3f39225cffd43a86d6cf8ff094fbabb2ac7e","tid":835780,"uid":25535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"就咁睇維基，佢最高學歷係清華化工系，仲要係推薦先入到。其實有無證據證明習近平嘅英文程度？<br />\n<br />\n我係到諗，如果習近平英文差，佢接觸到嘅資訊咪係得中文資訊同下面啲人翻譯左嘅報告。<br />\n<br />\n咁中文資訊就多數都係偏頗，而習近平用嘅人一直都係擦鞋仔多，係唔係代表習近平由細到大都係接觸偏頗嘅資訊，令到佢覺得中國真係好勁？"},{"pid":"53f85c310450716ad993448ebd92af7cc0da29e7","tid":835780,"uid":65024,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:56:29.000Z","msg":"屌！笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b11eeed74c425d442ccc420e12431c2c0a54eb","tid":835780,"uid":61464,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:59:17.000Z","msg":"點會唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9320b6d6752eede54830b6e3ac07029162274f96","tid":835780,"uid":75778,"like":37,"dislike":6,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"識，英文好過大部分連登仔"},{"pid":"1d9de6ff09e1e299b0e88747e1ac555b117b5bac","tid":835780,"uid":52581,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"呢個post會出現好多佢嘅同學啦，朋友啦，親戚啦，甚至乎青梅竹馬去證明佢嘅英文程度"},{"pid":"306c2dbcf6773923953e1548dd36224ac2e3f692","tid":835780,"uid":185449,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:02:14.000Z","msg":"識 X 同i 兩隻英文字就夠"},{"pid":"6e53e292ffda66b59d41fe61d43060de4edf14af","tid":835780,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:05:36.000Z","msg":"連手下馬雲都識英文啦"},{"pid":"bb675184cba1781483b97b31dd25640b1580e6c0","tid":835780,"uid":171791,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:10:53.000Z","msg":"諗都諗到有幾好啦<br />\n1）無收到正統中學教育 ，高考<br />\n2）清華讀化工 重有岩岩開放個陣 <br />\n3）無出過國<br />\n4）之前工作上唔使用英文，無做過對外既崗位"},{"pid":"15f78129bd4667167a2a8d50c24504987d38a732","tid":835780,"uid":31841,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"識就唔會俾咁多傻仔玩啦<br />\n江澤民胡撚塗就識"},{"pid":"6596d553adcab3ea13fccfeea95397e829aaf19d","tid":835780,"uid":176063,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74a252f6a59949ee54f051790cf9ae9c0c33f153","tid":835780,"uid":49197,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"我表哥同佢同屆,佢話習近平英文詞彙量起碼有10萬"},{"pid":"25b218ce8eb531c17b447a699e1a2dd75afef5a0","tid":835780,"uid":189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"後生嗰陣同老豆返鄉下耕田，淨係讀到小學，你話識唔識喇"},{"pid":"04cc58a04cf69db8f5fd4f7ee82d4f459239bb07","tid":835780,"uid":66686,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:19:15.000Z","msg":"中文都唔識啦<br />\n農同衣都搞錯"},{"pid":"adbd7ba89636db67d360a58f2f97cd45b0046acf","tid":835780,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"佢個女教返佢轉頭都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543084759521b8394e05680072528c79062de23a","tid":835780,"uid":57700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfe7f0ecccb518ebc56590852ac042d261f2d5f6","tid":835780,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1d9de6ff09e1e299b0e88747e1ac555b117b5bac","tid":835780,"uid":52581,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"呢個post會出現好多佢嘅同學啦，朋友啦，親戚啦，甚至乎青梅竹馬去證明佢嘅英文程度"},"citedBy":0,"repl